OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782386302
OL,3,CHosepipe ban announced for thousands
OL,4,Cof South East Water customers
OL,6,FA hosepipe ban has been announced for
OL,7,Fthousands of South East Water
OL,8,Fcustomers in Kent.
OL,10,FThe water company said the ban will
OL,11,Fcome officially on Friday (3 July) but
OL,12,Fis asking people to respect the ban
OL,13,F"with immediate effect".
OL,15,FIt means people should not use
OL,16,Fhosepipes for watering their gardens,
OL,17,Fwashing cars, patios and boats and
OL,18,Ffrom filling swimming and paddling
OL,19,Fpools.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
