CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782386302
OL,3,CHosepipe ban announced for thousands
OL,4,Cof South East Water customers
OL,6,FIt comes as the UK is experiencing a
OL,7,Fheatwave with the Met Office issuing a
OL,8,Fred warning for extreme heat which is
OL,9,Fin place until the end of Thursday (25
OL,10,FJune) and covers Kent.
OL,12,FSE Water said despite producing up to
OL,13,Fmore than an additional 100 million
OL,14,Flitres of water a day, demand for
OL,15,Fdrinking water needs to be reduced to
OL,16,Fensure that supply interruptions are
OL,17,Fnot experienced across its network
OL,18,Fthroughout the summer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782386302
OL,3,CHosepipe ban announced for thousands
OL,4,Cof South East Water customers
OL,6,FDavid Hinton, Chief Executive Officer,
OL,7,FSouth East Water, said: "We completely
OL,8,Funderstand why everyone reaches for
OL,9,Fthe hose when the weather gets this
OL,10,Fhot.
OL,12,F"It's natural to want to enjoy our
OL,13,Fgardens and cool down, and we know how
OL,14,Ffrustrating it is to hear that
OL,15,Frestrictions are coming into place.
OL,26,@oD@YOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782386302
OL,3,CHosepipe ban announced for thousands
OL,4,Cof South East Water customers
OL,6,F"Our teams have worked incredibly hard
OL,7,Fto prepare for this summer, but the
OL,8,Fsheer scale of this sustained heatwave
OL,9,Fmeans drinking water is being drawn
OL,10,Ffrom our storage tanks faster than it
OL,11,Fcan be treated and refilled.
OL,13,F"Our absolute priority has to be
OL,14,Fmaking sure there is always enough
OL,15,Fwater for everyone's essential daily
OL,16,Fneeds`like hygiene, drinking and
OL,17,Fcooking`and that we protect our
OL,18,Fvulnerable customers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782386302
OL,3,CHosepipe ban announced for thousands
OL,4,Cof South East Water customers
OL,6,F"To safeguard that shared supply and
OL,7,Fprevent any homes from facing a sudden
OL,8,Floss of water, we sadly need to ask
OL,9,Four communities to not use their
OL,10,Fhosepipes immediately.
OL,12,F"We are deeply sorry for the
OL,13,Fdisruption this causes, and we are
OL,14,Fincredibly grateful to everyone
OL,15,Fhelping us protect Kent's water."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
